1
00:00:48,370 --> 00:00:52,970
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,610 --> 00:00:56,060
[Episode 10]

3
00:01:02,790 --> 00:01:03,520
Are you ready to face

4
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,319
your destiny?

5
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:06,270
To be an ordinary person?

6
00:01:06,370 --> 00:01:07,700
It's still not too late.

7
00:01:07,870 --> 00:01:08,530
If you are willing to

8
00:01:08,530 --> 00:01:09,730
get rid of this child,

9
00:01:09,950 --> 00:01:11,870
your body might still recover.

10
00:01:12,350 --> 00:01:13,080
Get rid of it?

11
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:16,610
I'm just making a suggestion.

12
00:01:17,570 --> 00:01:19,370
It's your body and your destiny.

13
00:01:19,390 --> 00:01:20,990
You can do whatever you want.

14
00:01:21,450 --> 00:01:22,530
But being a mother

15
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,560
is quite nice too.

16
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:26,310
You'll be a good mom.

17
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:35,530
We're here.

18
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:38,570
Thanks for walking me back.

19
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:42,200
Aren't you going to
invite me in for a drink?

20
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,229
Sure.

21
00:01:43,729 --> 00:01:44,840
I just got some new red wine.

22
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,100
I'll mull some for you.

23
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:50,250
About my pregnancy,

24
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,080
don't tell Dongqing yet.

25
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,430
Zhao,

26
00:01:59,259 --> 00:01:59,990
have a drink.

27
00:02:00,930 --> 00:02:01,450
Yan,

28
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,280
I'm not really into mulled wine.

29
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:05,950
Drinking mulled wine makes me too hot.

30
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:06,680
You drink it.

31
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:07,870
Why is it

32
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:09,169
so hot in here today?

33
00:02:09,370 --> 00:02:10,000
Don't you feel it?

34
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,530
It's like a chimney in here.

35
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:12,280
Dongqing,

36
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,300
cheers.

37
00:02:25,010 --> 00:02:25,930
Dongqing,

38
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,910
you only prepared

39
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,700
these few snacks?

40
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,150
That's so boring.

41
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,370
I ordered some good food.

42
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,460
It'll be here soon.

43
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,630
Come in.

44
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,550
Mr. Zhao,

45
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:41,710
your food is here.

46
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:43,400
Chen?

47
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,400
Why are you delivering food?

48
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:46,680
It's mealtime,

49
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,360
and deliveries are slow.

50
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:50,560
Boss Tian was afraid you'd be starving,

51
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,710
so she sent me to deliver it.

52
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:55,079
Let me introduce you.

53
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:55,410
Okay.

54
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:58,030
He's just temping as a delivery guy.

55
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,030
He's a boss himself

56
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:00,680
and runs a plain noodle shop.

57
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,190
Those noodles taste amazing.

58
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:04,310
Your homemade soy sauce is delicious too.

59
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,360
It's a small business.

60
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,620
Just a small business.

61
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:09,960
Mr. Zhao.

62
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,290
Here.

63
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,730
Boss Tian has a message

64
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:14,190
for you.

65
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:15,430
What message?

66
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,680
Can we hear it?

67
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,710
I guess

68
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,190
you can.

69
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:22,570
Boss Tian said,

70
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:25,590
"Mr. Zhao hasn't come to my place

71
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:27,280
to eat for a while.

72
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,840
I kind of miss him.

73
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,520
Is he tired of my food

74
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,400
and going to

75
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:33,180
other places to eat?"

76
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:35,110
Isn't that vilifying me?

77
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,400
Can't I make something

78
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,200
to eat at home?

79
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,620
That's what I said too.

80
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,090
But Boss Tian said,

81
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:42,840
"Mr. Zhao is a bachelor

82
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,079
and doesn't like cooking.

83
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,630
Once he starts cooking for himself,

84
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:50,310
he must be attached
or interested in someone."

85
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,210
Then, to prove my innocence,

86
00:03:53,970 --> 00:03:54,910
should I go to the snail stall

87
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:56,360
in person tomorrow?

88
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:57,520
Absolutely.

89
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:58,960
All right, I won't disturb you anymore.

90
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,870
Okay, I'm off.

91
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:00,560
Thanks, Mr. Chen.

92
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,470
Okay, bye.

93
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,520
Enjoy your meal.

94
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:07,490
Come on.

95
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:07,960
Try it.

96
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:09,910
It smells so good.

97
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,970
Is it chicken soup?

98
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:12,190
Snail soup.

99
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:13,680
How is it?

100
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,310
It's delicious.

101
00:04:14,310 --> 00:04:15,870
Although this shop is small,

102
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:17,630
it's a century-old shop.

103
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,360
It smells so fishy.

104
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:21,560
It doesn't.

105
00:04:22,370 --> 00:04:24,040
Right. It doesn't taste fishy at all.

106
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,860
Only you think so.

107
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:27,190
Is there something wrong with your taste?

108
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:32,310
Then maybe there is
something wrong with my taste.

109
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:33,990
Zhao Hengzhi.

110
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,190
Is this Boss Tian

111
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,840
very pretty?

112
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,510
Not really pretty, just average.

113
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,580
But...

114
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:42,360
But what?

115
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,780
Hard to say.

116
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,000
Just drink the soup.

117
00:04:56,800 --> 00:05:01,000
[Snail]

118
00:05:02,050 --> 00:05:06,400
[Chapter 7: Snail Killing]

119
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:14,550
Boss Tian.

120
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:16,800
Mr. Zhao.

121
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,170
Long time no see.

122
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:21,240
Have a seat.

123
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,120
We're having steamed buns today.

124
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,050
Snail fillings.

125
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,290
With snail meat?

126
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:26,900
I've had radish,

127
00:05:26,930 --> 00:05:28,300
zucchini, broccoli,

128
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,270
seaweed, and seafood buns,

129
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:31,240
but never snail meat ones.

130
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:31,890
All right,

131
00:05:31,890 --> 00:05:33,490
give me 2 bowls of soup later.

132
00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:34,350
Two bowls?

133
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,200
You brought a friend?

134
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,120
A girl?

135
00:05:37,409 --> 00:05:38,430
A guy.

136
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,240
I asked you to buy milk tea.

137
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,290
Why did you get this?

138
00:05:43,290 --> 00:05:44,870
I suddenly really wanted to eat it.

139
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:45,270
Here.

140
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,390
It's fine if you want to eat it,

141
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:47,630
but you can't bring it
to someone else's shop.

142
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:48,630
-It’s fine.
-What's wrong with that?

143
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,270
This is from the barbecue shop

144
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:50,070
ahead, right?

145
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,040
I like it too.

146
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:53,450
Mr. Zhao, your friend

147
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,100
is really handsome.

148
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,659
Have a seat.

149
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,400
Director.

150
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,480
Hello, Director.

151
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:10,890
Where is Wang Fang?

152
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,850
She didn't come to work today.

153
00:06:14,550 --> 00:06:16,480
She didn't ask me for leave either.

154
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:19,680
She didn't ask for leave
and didn't reply to messages.

155
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,340
I even called her,

156
00:06:21,470 --> 00:06:23,130
but she didn't answer either.

157
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,930
Could something have happened to her?

158
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,630
Drink less milk tea.

159
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:28,560
It's unhealthy.

160
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,510
Okay, go back to work.

161
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:35,360
Ya.

162
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,920
I miss you so much.

163
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,159
Why would you?

164
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:43,020
We just saw each other yesterday.

165
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:52,159
Snail meat buns.

166
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,380
Th-This is a full snail feast.

167
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:55,430
I'm starting to get hungry again.

168
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:56,430
When can we start?

169
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,790
It's still too hot right now.

170
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,100
So in the meantime,

171
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,980
please wait for me a little longer.

172
00:07:02,980 --> 00:07:04,830
I've been busy at the stove all day.

173
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:07,060
Look, I'm covered in sweat.

174
00:07:07,330 --> 00:07:08,390
I'll go up and change clothes.

175
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:09,450
I'll be right back.

176
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,580
Wait for me.

177
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:12,080
Okay.

178
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,720
People used to talk about the Tofu Beauty.

179
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,560
Look at her,

180
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,160
she can be the Snail Beauty.

181
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,750
I didn't notice that.

182
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:29,070
What do you think
a legendary beauty looks like?

183
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:29,750
Gentle,

184
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,210
capable,

185
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,420
and very charming.

186
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:34,680
Anyway,

187
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,870
she's the kind of woman men really want

188
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:37,130
to marry and take home.

189
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:40,140
Dongqing,
you're a big pervert, aren't you?

190
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:42,240
Don't forget you have a wife.

191
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,190
Of course.

192
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:45,040
I'm strictly disciplined.

193
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,200
I forgot to report to my wife.

194
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:52,830
Okay,

195
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:54,900
I got it.

196
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:56,970
Come back early after dinner.

197
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,550
Bye-bye.

198
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:01,900
If you have nothing to do,

199
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:03,030
have dinner with me.

200
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:53,810
Drink some.

201
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:56,590
I'm not good at drinking liquor.

202
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,150
This is Boss Tian's hospitality.

203
00:08:58,150 --> 00:08:58,810
Drink some.

204
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,510
Okay.

205
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,090
No going home

206
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,500
until we're drunk.

207
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,980
Steak from Florence.

208
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:10,240
Dry-aged for 30 days.

209
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,100
The best steak,

210
00:09:11,390 --> 00:09:12,450
better than Wagyu.

211
00:09:12,450 --> 00:09:13,630
Wagyu has too much fat.

212
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:14,560
It's too greasy.

213
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,070
Come on, cheers.

214
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:21,980
Yuanji?

215
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:27,200
Isn't he with Wang Fang?

216
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,200
Yuanji!

217
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,200
Yuanji!

218
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:33,830
Yuanji!

219
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,080
Yuanji!

220
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:38,750
Who is she?

221
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,340
Who are you?

222
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:41,760
You...

223
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,170
Yuanji is my boyfriend.

224
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:44,000
You shameless

225
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,720
woman!

226
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,120
You...

227
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,360
Miss,

228
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:49,400
who are you?

229
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,670
What are you doing?

230
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,620
Are you crazy?

231
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:03,600
Are you okay?

232
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:05,360
Let go of me!

233
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:06,940
Let go of me!

234
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,510
-Let go of me!
-Wait!

235
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:15,760
Let go of her!

236
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:16,920
Director.

237
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,680
Take her to my room.

238
00:10:20,210 --> 00:10:20,870
-Yes.
-Yes.

239
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:27,450
Your dating time

240
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,440
is over.

241
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:29,870
Over?

242
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,240
Although he exists

243
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,150
in this world,

244
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,240
he's only a 2D character.

245
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:37,040
His memory of you

246
00:10:37,310 --> 00:10:39,030
has been cleared by the system.

247
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,490
But my Affection Level...

248
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:41,960
I spent so much money on it.

249
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:44,120
You have already been rewarded.

250
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:47,590
I can renew the Affection Level.

251
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:48,370
Wang Fang,

252
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,630
this is just a game.

253
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:51,080
Game over.

254
00:10:52,790 --> 00:10:53,510
I don't want that.

255
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:54,630
I only want Yuanji.

256
00:10:55,030 --> 00:10:55,760
Lady Yuzhen,

257
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,560
please think of a way.

258
00:10:57,770 --> 00:10:58,960
I only want Yuanji.

259
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,360
I don't want anyone else.

260
00:11:07,150 --> 00:11:07,880
Lady Yuzhen.

261
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:10,440
Lady Yuzhen, Lady Yuzhen!

262
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,600
Please, please,

263
00:11:12,780 --> 00:11:14,180
make Yuanji remember me.

264
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,600
He clearly loved me so much.

265
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:30,820
Wang Fang.

266
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:32,790
Lady Yuzhen!

267
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,390
Lady Yuzhen...

268
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:38,720
Cheers!

269
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:55,510
Boss Tian.

270
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:57,900
This all-snail feast

271
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,520
is quite delicious.

272
00:11:59,990 --> 00:12:01,560
You were drinking happily.

273
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:03,540
Why did you suddenly start crying?

274
00:12:06,770 --> 00:12:07,810
Here, a tissue.

275
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,020
I'm sorry, you two.

276
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,740
I made a fool of myself.

277
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,510
Living in this world

278
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,390
itself

279
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,710
is tied to suffering.

280
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,860
Why did I say that?

281
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,700
Just to fit the occasion, I guess.

282
00:12:34,390 --> 00:12:35,000
Zhao Li?

283
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,270
How many times have I told you?

284
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,000
I am not Zhao Li.

285
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,810
Did this Zhao Li

286
00:12:43,980 --> 00:12:45,080
owe you a lot of money

287
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,360
or hurt you deeply?

288
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:47,870
I am Zhao Hengzhi.

289
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,740
Zhao Hengzhi!

290
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:05,860
The men here are handsome,

291
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:08,080
but the women are plain-looking,

292
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,490
just like Wang Fang.

293
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:11,330
Why did you do this?

294
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:13,200
I'm saving these women.

295
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,290
I let them gain it first,

296
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,410
